odase

Interface TBoxModel


  • public interface TBoxModel
    TBoxModel allows to find ontology classes, properties, domain, range, etc. TBoxModel implementation should be sound but don't have to be complete. So, it is correct to return only partial answers.

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Interface and Description
      static class  TBoxModel.TBoxOwlClass
      TBoxOwlClass represents an owl Class on which tbox reasoning can be done
      static class  TBoxModel.TBoxProperty
      TBoxProperty represents an owl property (data or object) on which tbox reasoning can be done
